        </script><div class="caas-body"><p>Argentinian soccer legend Lionel Messi's clothing brand The Messi Store made its U.S. market debut on Friday, with the stock jumping more than 200% before falling back below its initial price by the market close.</p><p>MGO Global Inc. (<a href="https://finance.yahoo.com/quote/MGOL?p=MGOL&.tsrc=fin-srch" data-ylk="slk:MGOL;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas" class="link " data-rapid_p="14" data-v9y="0">MGOL</a>), the operator of The Messi Store, Argentinian soccer star Lionel Messis clothing brand, sold just 1.5 million shares to the public, though trading was halted multiple times during the morning session as investors flocked to Messis brand.</p><div class="caas-da "><div data-wf-benji-page-context="{"pageUrl":"https://finance.yahoo.com/news/messi-tied-clothing-stock-jumps-more-than-200-after-ipo-closes-lower-in-wild-first-day-of-trading-173536853.html","spaceid":"1183300001","site":"finance","hashtag":"news;$mgol;yftickers;investments;finance","lmsid":"a077000000BAh3wAAD","lpstaid":"dad32002-ab15-4e75-bb5e-69d2a79e1d68","pct":"storywithleadvideo"}" data-wf-benji-wafer-config="{"updateI13n":true}" data-wf-benji-config="{"positions":{"INARTICLE-dad32002-ab15-4e75-bb5e-69d2a79e1d681717468768125":{"id":"INARTICLE-dad32002-ab15-4e75-bb5e-69d2a79e1d681717468768125","path":"/22888152279/us/yfin/ros/dt/us_yfin_ros_dt_mid_center","region":"index","size":[[970,350],[728,90],[970,250],"fluid"],"kvs":{"loc":"mid_center"},"refresh":{"reserved":{"duration":1e+23}}}}}" id="sda-INARTICLE-dad32002-ab15-4e75-bb5e-69d2a79e1d681717468768125" class="caas-sda-benji-ad wafer-destroyed" data-wf-trigger="onLoad" data-wf-margin="100 0" data-hide-ad-string=""><div id="INARTICLE-dad32002-ab15-4e75-bb5e-69d2a79e1d681717468768125" class="wafer-benji-success" data-google-query-id="CIOztOD1wIYDFXajfwQdSxoG-g" style="min-height: 90px;"><div id="google_ads_iframe_/22888152279/us/yfin/ros/dt/us_yfin_ros_dt_mid_center_0__container__" style="border: 0pt none; The brand is centered on "leveraging" fame into potential retail opportunities.</p><p>We are a performance-driven lifestyle brand portfolio company focused on strategically leveraging the fame, celebrity power and global social media influence of world-class athletes, entertainers, and other cultural icons to create fresh, modern, and compelling product and apparel brands aligned with and inspired by the values, personal styles, and aspirations of our valued brand partners, the company <a href="https://www.mgoglobalinc.com/investor-relations/" rel="nofollow noopener" target="_blank" data-ylk="slk:wrote;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas" class="link " data-rapid_p="15" data-v9y="0">wrote</a> on its investor relations page.</p><p>Messis name has likely had an impact on the stock.
